## AQA pseudocode reference
Compare your C++ with how AQA would express the same class:

```
class Animal
    private name
    private sound
    private age

    public procedure new(givenName, givenSound, givenAge)
        name ← givenName
        sound ← givenSound
        age ← givenAge
    endprocedure

    public function getName()
        return name
    endfunction
endclass
```

The concepts are identical — only the syntax differs.
